components.name: AppComponent
components.templateData:
<matxtnd-loading-button mat-raised-button [busy]="true">
  <matxtnd-loading-button-ready>
    Update
  </matxtnd-loading-button-ready>
  <matxtnd-loading-button-busy>
    Updating...
  </matxtnd-loading-button-busy>
</matxtnd-loading-button>


<matxtnd-loading-message>
  Loading...
</matxtnd-loading-message>

<matxtnd-swoosh-animation></matxtnd-swoosh-animation>

<button mat-button color="primary" (click)="successSnackbar()">Display Success SnackBar</button>
